> Announcing the First Annual Great North American Extreme Bus Race 
> 
> You are invited to participate in the First Annual Great North American Extreme 
> Bus Race coming up May 26, 2007. 
> 
> Rules: exceeding the speed limit is allowed if you're able. Engine must be a 
> stock 1.6, 1.7, 1.8, or 2.0L air-cooled VW motor. Crews will consist of 
> 2-person teams. Busses will be issued a GPS locating device before the race 
> begins and will be tracked from race-central in Chattanooga. Busses are allowed 
> only 16 hours/day of continuous driving. A mandatory 8-hour rest period is 
> required per 24 hours. Teams can choose any route they choose but must have 
> proper documentation to get into Canada. 
> 
